    <Feature>
      <Keywords />
      <Name>Voice of Authority</Name>
      <Text>You can invoke the power of law to claim authority over others. Once per turn when you target an ally with a 1st level or higher spell, that ally can use their reaction to make a single melee or ranged weapon attack against a target of your choice. If a single spell targets multiple allies, only one ally gains this benefit.</Text>
